body:
On 6/3/07, Chas Owens  wrote:
snip
> my $tidy = "/usr/bin/tidy";
> my @tidy_args = qw(--foo --bar -- example);
> my $path = get_path();
> my $file = $path . get_file();
>
> system($tidy, @tidy_args, $file);

Opps, forgot the error checking.

system($tidy, @tidy_args, $file)
    or die qq("$tidy @tidy_args $file" failed: $?";

